  <td valign=3Dtop style=3D'padding:0in 5.75pt 0in 5.75pt'>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Space Ports are bases that provide many important servi=
ces
  for your empire. For normal planetary empires, space ports must always be=
 built
  at a colony. However pirate factions may build space ports at any locatio=
n.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>They serve as a central point of trade for your empire.
  Mined resources are brought here by freighters and mining ships.<o:p></o:=
p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Space Ports also provide construction facilities for yo=
ur
  empire. Both state and private ships are built here. When private citizens
  purchase freighters or other ships, your empire earns income.<o:p></o:p><=
/span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Space Ports also provide other vital functions:<o:p></o=
:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoListParagraphCxSpFirst style=3D'text-indent:-.25in;mso-list=
:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span
  lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;
  mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-no-proof:yes'><sp=
an
  style=3D'mso-list:Ignore'>&middot;<span style=3D'font:7.0pt "Times New Ro=
man"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  </span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-langu=
age:
  EN-GB;mso-no-proof:yes'>Heavy weapons provide strong defense for the colo=
ny</span><span
  lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",seri=
f;
  mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'> </span><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-lan=
guage:
  EN-GB;mso-no-proof:yes'><o:p></o:p></span></p>
  <p class=3DMsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style=3D'text-indent:-.25in;mso-lis=
t:l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span
  lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;
